# Remote Functions

- Location: `src/lib/remotes/{entity}.remote.ts` — **never** under `src/lib/server/`
- Types: `query` (read), `form` (create/update), `command` (delete)
- Validated inputs: Zod schema as **first argument** to `query`/`form`/`command`
- After mutations: `void relatedQuery().refresh()`; use `redirect()` after create/update forms
- Implementation: call service functions only — no direct Drizzle in remotes

